68
00:03:25,855 --> 00:03:26,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Diam kau, berengsek!</font>

69
00:03:28,225 --> 00:03:29,226
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga.</font>

70
00:03:29,526 --> 00:03:33,762
<font color=#FFFF00>Bocah, kau itu tipe yang bikin masalah dengan mulutmu.</font>

