83
00:04:10,467 --> 00:04:12,469
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pasti sangat sibuk hari ini.</font>

84
00:04:13,336 --> 00:04:14,537
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah makan?</font>

85
00:04:26,516 --> 00:04:29,319
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau harus menahannya sampai jam segini?
Apa yang kau pikirkan?</font>

86
00:04:30,020 --> 00:04:31,187
