- Pergilah.</font>

182
00:08:52,749 --> 00:08:54,217
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana bisa menyuruhnya pergi?</font>

183
00:08:54,484 --> 00:08:55,884
<font color=#FFFF00>Mu Yeong-ah!</font>

184
00:08:55,885 --> 00:08:57,754
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga, padahal aku hendak membantunya.</font>

185
00:08:58,187 --> 00:09:00,856
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi, apa yang sudah Mu Yeong lakukan...</font>

186
00:09:00,857 --> 00:09:02,958
<font color=#FFFF00>...sampai bisa mendapat kesaksian
