187
00:09:02,959 --> 00:09:04,027
<font color=#FFFF00>Tutup mulutmu!</font>

188
00:09:04,127 --> 00:09:05,127
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian semua mendengarnya, 'kan?</font>

189
00:09:05,128 --> 00:09:07,997
<font color=#FFFF00>Han Mu Yeong kita khawatirkan nanti,
