190
00:09:08,264 --> 00:09:09,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Na Rae, ambil mobil.</font>

191
00:09:09,499 --> 00:09:13,835
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian lakukan yang terbaik agar dia jangan sampai berubah pikiran.</font>

192
00:09:13,836 --> 00:09:14,937
<font color=#FFFF00>- Oke?
- Oke!</font>

193
00:09:14,938 --> 00:09:16,872
<font color=#FFFF00>- Bergerak!
- Ayo bergerak!</font>

194
00:09:16,873 --> 00:09:17,907
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo pergi!</font>

195
00:09:18,508 --> 00:09:20,643
<font color=#FFFF00>(Pecundang Surat Kabar Daehan : Lee Suk Min)</font>

196
00:09:21,578 --> 00:09:23,178
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sedang sibuk! Mau apa kau meneleponku?</font>

197
00:09:23,179 --> 00:09:24,259
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Mu Yeong sekarang di mana?</i></font>

198
00:09:24,447 --> 00:09:25,747
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kenapa aku tidak bisa menghubunginya?</i></font>

199
00:09:25,748 --> 00:09:26,783
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau kau tahu di mana dia,</font>

200
00:09:27,317 --> 00:09:29,319
<font color=#FFFF00>apa kau berniat mengeluarkannya atau bagaimana?</font>

201
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,354
<font color=#FFFF00>"Mengeluarkannya"?</font>

202
00:09:31,888 --> 00:09:32,989
<font color=#FFFF00>Di mana sebenarnya dia?</font>

203
00:09:38,828 --> 00:09:39,829
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Jurnalis Han.</i></font>

204
00:09:41,164 --> 00:09:42,298
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku tidak bisa melakukannya.</i></font>

205
00:09:57,013 --> 00:09:58,047
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Seon Woo-ya!</i></font>

206
00:09:58,648 --> 00:09:59,649
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Yoon Seon Woo!</i></font>

207
00:10:33,216 --> 00:10:37,654
<font color=#FFFF00>(Supermarket Chungbuk)</font>

208
00:10:41,958 --> 00:10:43,159
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah, astaga.</font>

209
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:46,596
<font color=#FFFF00>Beberapa orang mungkin akan mengira usahanya berjalan lancar.</font>

210
00:10:51,267 --> 00:10:53,469
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Saat pertama kali bertemu, aku bertanya padamu.</i></font>

211
00:10:54,103 --> 00:10:57,106
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tidak peduli semenakutkan apa pun lawanmu,
