296
00:16:17,326 --> 00:16:19,428
<font color=#FFFF00>(Jaksa Kwon So Ra)</font>

297
00:16:19,528 --> 00:16:20,862
<font color=#FFFF00>(Penemuan dalam kasus)</font>

298
00:16:20,863 --> 00:16:23,365
<font color=#FFFF00>(Nama : Yoon Seon Woo,
