00:17:58,027 --> 00:17:59,427
<font color=#FFFF00>(Pemanggilan Saksi)</font>

322
00:17:59,428 --> 00:18:00,596
<font color=#FFFF00>(Saksi : Im Jae Tae)</font>

323
00:18:01,897 --> 00:18:02,997
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu namaku.</font>

324
00:18:02,998 --> 00:18:04,066
<font color=#FFFF00>(Saksi : Im Jae Tae)</font>

325
00:18:04,667 --> 00:18:05,667
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa-apaan ini?</font>

326
00:18:05,668 --> 00:18:09,438
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya adalah Anjing pemburu handal, Pak.
